{"tid":1979502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗咬狗］天水圍休班警食肆消夜 兩警打交傷及女同袍","createTime":"2020-04-19T12:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T15:35:31.000Z","uid":239336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b3241eb1f30004f3a6d9593e594e4b4bbaceaf","tid":1979502,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"凌晨5時36分，據報隷屬天水圍軍裝巡邏小隊的10名休班警員，在元朗屏會街一間食肆的店外分3張枱坐食消夜。10人包括4名沙展及6名警員，其間當中1名沙展與1名警員因事爭執，大打出手。該名沙展爆樽施襲，混亂中一名女警勸止時意外受傷，頭部受傷。<br />\n<br />\n惟警方衝鋒隊同元朗巡邏隊到場時，各人已四散離去，只剩下受傷女警，她送院經敷治後獲兩日病假休息。警方稱，事發時一名女子報警稱被一名男子襲擊。警方到場將一名女傷者送博愛醫院，案件列襲擊處理，天水圍警區指揮官正就此事進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200419/NSMAYQKCC53YURQZKNVOMKBCFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200419%2FNSMAYQKCC53YURQZKNVOMKBCFU%2F&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=6a00e177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200419%2FNSMAYQKCC53YURQZKNVOMKBCFU%2F&h=834ca7e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200419/NSMAYQKCC53YURQZKNVOMKBCFU/</a>"},{"pid":"8be72c2da9e70064025033d9a134c99c8b3d96bb","tid":1979502,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97f5cded40bd337bd321941f7c8d9d251e90c55","tid":1979502,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c2271a407388201be6e3822188ab2d5db6a9604","tid":1979502,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji